1
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:15,920
You know what?

2
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,879
I dreamed of you.

3
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:21,040
You in my dream

4
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:24,120
was so clear.

5
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:26,680
Sorry

6
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,200
for waking you up.

7
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:33,079
I wish I could keep seeing clearly like this.

8
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,920
Your eyes will fully recover tomorrow,

9
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,000
and you'll be able to return to your bright

10
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,599
and beautiful self.

11
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:44,640
I'll witness you becoming

12
00:01:45,079 --> 00:01:46,680
to become the best photographer.

13
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,359
Jiang Yue

14
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,560
I really like you.

15
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,240
I'm sorry.

16
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,759
I may not be able to accompany you.

17
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,439
For your safety,

18
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,800
I have to figure out

19
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,360
the totem and the key.

20
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:47,599
Jiang Yue, Jiang Yue.

21
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,400
Jiang Yue.

22
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,319
Jiang Yue.

23
00:02:58,199 --> 00:03:00,199
Professor Chu, where's Jiang Yue?

24
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,639
He went to find Jiang Changfa.

25
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,319
It's a family matter.

26
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:06,680
Let them solve it themselves.

27
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,280
I'll go find him.

28
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:08,960
Lu Qi.

29
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,400
Let me show you something.

30
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:14,680
Have a seat.

31
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,719
This is SP.

32
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:19,800
The International Fashion Organization awarded you the Rookie Award.

33
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,400
It will make your resume shine.

34
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,360
Are you happy?

35
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:31,240
But

36
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,159
the person who helped me get this award

37
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:34,000
left without saying goodbye.

38
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,080
I'll go find him.

39
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,400
Since you've already seen him,

40
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,439
why let him go?

41
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,840
Do you want me to die faster?

42
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,159
It's my fault.

43
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:54,199
I'm willing to be punished.

44
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:54,840
Punishment?

45
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,680
What punishment?

46
00:03:58,479 --> 00:03:59,719
How many lives do you have?

47
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:01,479
I accept.

48
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:07,680
Watch out!

49
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:30,920
Gao Qiao!

50
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,199
Gao Qiao!

51
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,920
Have someone clean this up.

52
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,480
News from Duke County says

53
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,959
the boss has issued a Sacrificial Decree against you.

54
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:04,079
Jiang Yue,

55
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,839
you want to run away with Lu Qi

56
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,680
even if you have to fight with me, right?

57
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:14,120
What's wrong?

58
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,600
Why are you back?

59
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,199
Are you showing off?

60
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,279
Leave if you don't want to see me.

61
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,279
Stop.

62
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,439
Gao Qiao is dead.

63
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:28,720
You killed him?

64
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,720
Who do you think killed her?

65
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:33,279
Jiang Yue.

66
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,959
No matter what,

67
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,600
we are family.

68
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:39,079
We rise and fall

69
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:41,199
together. You know that.

70
00:06:41,319 --> 00:06:42,240
That's why I'm back.

71
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,240
What do you want me to do?

72
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,240
Just tell me. I can help you.

73
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:48,360
Get everything the 3Z Group has lost

74
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,319
back for me.

75
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,040
and avenge

76
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,800
your mother and Gao Qiao.

77
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,160
Stop everything you're working on.

78
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:08,240
Focus on reversing

79
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,560
the negative news about 3Z Group online.

80
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,199
Release the news that Black Snow

81
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:14,120
hired killers to cause trouble at the exhibition.

82
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,040
Cover it up.

83
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,319
Within two days,

84
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,600
get me the list of all personnel

85
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:23,759
collaborating with Black Snow.

86
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,040
Pay them three times the price to get them over here.

87
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:34,319
Let the news out that we have signed contracts

88
00:07:34,879 --> 00:07:36,560
with those internationally renowned artists.

89
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,680
Don't make it vague.

90
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,519
It's the day after tomorrow.

91
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:44,839
Young Master Jiang.

92
00:07:45,279 --> 00:07:46,519
Do we have anything else to talk about?

93
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:47,519
Ms. Lin.

94
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,800
You are a famous artist of Dark Imagism.

95
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,639
Killer Butterfly on the Dark Web

96
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:53,560
should be able to give you a lot of advice.

97
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,639
Can you ask him to contact me?

98
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:24,040
Good.

99
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,040
That's my son.

100
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:32,600
If there's nothing else,

101
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,600
I'll go out.

102
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:34,600
Wait.

103
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:53,360
Who is this?

104
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,320
His name is Paul Gourmand.

105
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:56,600
He's a tobacco seller.

106
00:08:57,960 --> 00:09:00,120
He'll return to Duke County on the 28th of this month.

107
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,720
You go to see him off that day.

108
00:09:03,519 --> 00:09:05,759
3Z has never had any dealings with tobacco companies.

109
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:06,960
Tobacco?

110
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:09,519
It's probably a cover for human trafficking.

111
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:28,279
Qi.

112
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:28,879
Mom.

113
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,279
You're back.

114
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,360
How are you?

115
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,000
Are your eyes healed?

116
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,360
It's fine. All healed.

117
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,840
Qi, you're back.

118
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:39,840
Uncle.

119
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:43,039
Jiang Yue.

120
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:47,120
We haven't been together in ages.

121
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,799
Now that you're back,

122
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,720
let's have a family dinner.

123
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:04,279
Why did you leave without saying goodbye?

124
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:08,440
Jiang Yue, answer me.

125
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:09,519
Jiang Yue,

126
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,840
what are you waiting for?

127
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:15,200
Take your sister home.

128
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,080
I'm going to meet a friend.

129
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:27,720
You guys eat.

130
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,399
You're quite the smooth operator,

131
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:54,360
using my name out there.

132
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:58,919
Consider me in your debt.

133
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:02,440
Did you keep an eye on Lu Qi?

134
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,559
I did.

135
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,519
You didn't.

136
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:05,720
Do you believe that?

137
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,360
No.

138
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,279
Did you find out

139
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:13,320
The key?

140
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,159
No.

141
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:15,639
I knew it.

142
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,519
Jiang Changfa is a meticulous person.

143
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,720
Let alone

144
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,320
the key only exists in his mind.

145
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,600
Even if you trust him,

146
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,679
it's hard to get it.

147
00:11:28,879 --> 00:11:30,200
Since you don't want to kill him,

148
00:11:30,879 --> 00:11:31,879
you have to try your best.

149
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:35,120
You can't have any worries.

150
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:38,320
I mean Lu Qi.

151
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,720
Whether it's to keep her from affecting you,

152
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,919
or for her safety,

153
00:11:45,039 --> 00:11:46,279
you have to push her away.

154
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,320
Only in this way can you carry it out well.

155
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,320
Paul Gourmand.

156
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,919
Xavier Lian is a human trafficker.

157
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,399
When he was killed,

158
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:07,159
we found that

159
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,200
Paul Gourmand is his big boss.

160
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,519
In Europe,

161
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:14,120
he is a famous philanthropist.

162
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:16,360
Who gave this to you?

163
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,440
Jiang Changfa.

164
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,559
So he gave your father the key.

165
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:24,759
He also likes to issue the Sacrificial Decree.

166
00:12:26,279 --> 00:12:27,559
He will kill whoever is useless.

167
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:28,159
Yes.

168
00:12:30,679 --> 00:12:31,840
I see.
